\c 19
\s Ukuhlalisana kwabathatheneyo
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uJesu eseqedile lawomazwi\x + Mark. 10.1-12.\x*, wasuka eGalili\x + 17.22.\x*, weza emikhawulweni yeJudiya ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + Joha. 10.40; 11.7. Luka 9.51; 17.11.\x*.
\v 2 Amaxuku amakhulu asemlandela, wasewasilisa lapho\x + 12.15.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Basebesiza kuye abaFarisi bemlinga, bathi kuye: Kuvunyelwe yini ukuthi indoda yale umkayo ngaso sonke isizatho\x + 5.31.\x*?
\v 4 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Kalifundanga yini ukuthi owa\add ba\add*dabula kusukela ekuqaleni wabenza owesilisa lowesifazana\x + Gen. 1.27; 5.2.\x*?
\v 5 Wasesithi: Ngenxa yalokhu indoda izatshiya uyise lonina, inamathele kumkayo\x + Gen. 2.24. Efe. 5.31.\x*; labo ababili bazakuba nyamanye.
\v 6 Ngakho kabasebabili, kodwa \add sebe\add*nyamanye. Ngakho lokho uNkulunkulu akuhlanganisileyo kakungabi lamuntu okwehlukanisayo\x + 1 Kor. 6.16. Mal. 2.15. 1 Kor. 7.2.\x*.
\v 7 Bathi kuye: Pho uMozisi walayelani ukunika incwadi yesehlukaniso, lokumala\x + 5.31. Dute. 24.1.\x*?
\v 8 Wathi kubo: Ngenxa yobulukhuni benhliziyo zenu uMozisi walivumela ukwala omkenu\x + Mark. 16.14. Mark. 3.5; 6.52.\x*; kodwa kusukela ekuqaleni kwakungenjalo.
\v 9 Kodwa ngithi kini: Loba ngubani owala umkakhe, ngaphandle kokufeba, abesethatha omunye, uyafeba; futhi othatha owaliweyo uyafeba\x + 5.32.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Abafundi bathi kuye: Uba udaba lomuntu lomfazi lunjalo, akusizi ukuthatha\x + Zaga 21.19.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa wathi kubo: Kakusibo bonke\x + 1 Kor. 7.2,7,9.\x* abangalemukela lelilizwi\x + 19.12. 2 Kor. 7.2.\x*, ngaphandle kwabakunikiweyo\x + 13.11.\x*\x + 20.23.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba kukhona abathenwa, abazalwa benjalo kusukela esiswini sikanina; njalo kukhona abathenwa, abathenwa ngabantu\x + 2 Kho. 20.18. Gen. 37.36.\x*; kukhona futhi abathenwa, abazithenileyo ngenxa yombuso wamazulu\x + 5.29. 1 Kor. 7.32; 9.5,15.\x*. Lowo ongakwemukela \add lokho\add* ka\add kwa\add*mukele\x + 19.12. 2 Kor. 7.2.\x*.
\s Ukubusiswa kwabantwana abancane
\p
\v 13 Khona kwalethwa kuye abantwana abancane, ukuze abeke izandla \add zakhe\add* phezu kwabo, akhuleke\x + Luka 18.15-17. Mark. 10.13-16.\x*; kodwa abafundi babakhuza.
\v 14 Kodwa uJesu wathi: Vumelani abantwana abancane, lingabenqabeli ukuza kimi; ngoba umbuso wamazulu ungowabanje\x + 18.3.\x*.
\v 15 Wasebeka izandla phezu kwabo, wasuka lapho.
\s Ijaha elinothileyo
\p
\v 16 Njalo khangela, kwasondela omunye wathi kuye\x + Mark. 10.17-31. Luka 18.18-30.\x*: Mfundisi olungileyo, ngizakwenzani okulungileyo, ukuze ngibe lempilo elaphakade?
\v 17 Wasesithi kuye: Ungibizelani ngokuthi olungileyo? Kakho olungileyo, ngaphandle koyedwa, uNkulunkulu\x + Luka 10.25-28.\x*. Kodwa uba uthanda ukungena ekuphileni, gcina imilayo\x + Levi 18.5. Neh. 9.29.\x*.
\v 18 Wathi kuye: Yiyiphi? UJesu wasesithi: Ungabulali; ungafebi; ungebi; ungafakazi amanga\x + Eks. 20.12-16. Dute. 5.16-20. Roma 13.9.\x*;
\v 19 hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko\x + 15.4.\x*; njalo, wothanda umakhelwane wakho njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\x + 22.39. Levi 19.18. Luka 10.27.\x*\add*.
\v 20 Ijaha lathi kuye: Konke lokhu ngikugcinile kusukela ebutsheni bami; ngisaswelani?
\v 21 UJesu wathi kulo: Uba uthanda ukuphelela\x + 5.48.\x*, hamba uthengise impahla zakho uphe abayanga\x + Luka 12.33. Luka 16.9. Seb. 2.45; 4.34,35. 1 Tim. 6.17-19.\x*, njalo uzakuba lempahla eligugu ezulwini\x + 6.20.\x*; njalo uze lapha, ungilandele.
\v 22 Kodwa selizwile lelilizwi ijaha lasuka lidanile; ngoba lalilempahla ezinengi.
\p
\v 23 UJesu wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Onothileyo uzangena ngokulukhuni embusweni wamazulu\x + 13.22. 1 Tim. 6.9,10. Hez. 33.31.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo futhi ngithi kini: Kulula ukuthi\x + Mark. 10.24.\x* ikamela lingene ngentunja yenalithi, kulokuthi onothileyo angene embusweni wezulu\x + 23.24.\x*.
\v 25 Sebezwile abafundi bakhe bamangala kakhulu, bathi: Pho kungasindiswa bani?
\v 26 Kodwa uJesu wa\add ba\add*khangela wathi kubo: Kubantu kakulakwenzeka\x + Mark. 10.21,27.\x*, kodwa kuNkulunkulu zonke izinto zingenzeka\x + Jobe 42.2. Mark. 10.27; 14.36. Luka 1.37; 18.27. Gen. 18.14.\x*.
\s Umvuzo wokuzidela
\p
\v 27 Khona uPetro waphendula wathi kuye: Khangela, thina sitshiye konke sakulandela; pho sizazuzani\x + 4.22.4.20. Mark. 1.18. Luka 5.11. Dute. 33.9.\x*?
\v 28 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Lina elingilandeleyo, ekuvuselelweni lapho iNdodana yomuntu isihlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi senkazimulo yayo\x + Tit. 3.5. Joha. 3.3,5. 1 Pet. 1.23.\x*, lani lizahlala ezihlalweni zobukhosi ezilitshumi lambili\x + Luka 22.30. Isam. 3.21; 20.4.\x* lahlulele izizwe ezilitshumi lambili zakoIsrayeli\x + 20.21. 1 Kor. 6.2.Isam. 2.26.\x*.
\v 29 Laye wonke otshiye izindlu, kumbe abafowabo, kumbe odadewabo, kumbe uyise, kumbe unina, kumbe umkakhe, kumbe abantwana, kumbe amasimu, ngenxa yebizo lami, uzakwemukela ngekhulu, adle ilifa lempilo elaphakade\x + 4.20.4.22. Mark. 1.18. Luka 5.11. Dute. 33.9.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa abanengi abokuqala bazakuba ngabokucina\x + 20.16. Mark. 10.31. Luka 13.30.\x*, labokucina ngabokuqala\x + 21.31,32.\x*.